{"tid":2026744,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"「PETA」投稿《動物森友會》影片包圍傅達博物館抗議，呼籲解放魚類回歸大海","createTime":"2020-05-21T06:55:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T08:13:19.000Z","uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"13994a488d027674a7ac16b1b7cf8015731963eb","tid":2026744,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:55:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbor.4gamers.com.tw/rzK-SNJQxxffHFLJCJNuLQzZOyA=/filters:watermark(https://img.4gamers.com.tw/default-image/4gamers_watermark_20190925.png,-5,-3,0,17):format(jpeg):quality(90)/https%3A%2F%2Fimg.4gamers.com.tw%2Fpuku-clone-version%2Ff0eff8d150ffee7977d5ddd143d4b61b-4200152583c7a29ba35b12e7b8bc9e95a3a97a9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbor.4gamers.com.tw%2FrzK-SNJQxxffHFLJCJNuLQzZOyA%3D%2Ffilters%3Awatermark%28https%3A%2F%2Fimg.4gamers.com.tw%2Fdefault-image%2F4gamers_watermark_20190925.png%2C-5%2C-3%2C0%2C17%29%3Aformat%28jpeg%29%3Aquality%2890%29%2Fhttps%253A%252F%252Fimg.4gamers.com.tw%252Fpuku-clone-version%252Ff0eff8d150ffee7977d5ddd143d4b61b-4200152583c7a29ba35b12e7b8bc9e95a3a97a9a.jpg&h=c102b9c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「PETA」善待動物組織向來是遊戲社群最熟悉的動物保護團體，因為他們經常針對遊戲裡的「虛擬動物」來提倡動物保護與全素理念。繼上次在官網中發文呼籲玩家不要在《集合啦！動物森友會》（Animal Crossing New Horizon）遊戲中捉蟲捕魚後，這回 PETA 投稿抖音（TikTok）影片，以更盛大的行動宣揚組織理念：包圍博物館抗議。<br />\n <br />\n根據 PETA 近日的官方推特貼文，你會發現一群身穿 DIY 設計成 PETA 服裝的玩家們大舉突襲傅達所在的博物館，不但圍繞在傅達身旁或是水族箱前面，拼命作表情動作與發話「解放水族箱」，最後還在博物館前方擺設標語呼籲「魚兒屬於大海」，讓一切的畫面相當逗趣。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，早在《動物森友會》上市之初就能看出 PETA 組織的人也相當熱愛這款遊戲，最初他們在全素指南的公告中呼籲玩家不要捉蟲或捕魚，也不要建造博物館等，希望玩家發揮同理心與愛心，理解善待動物所創造出的美好世界。PETA 甚至希望玩家接受被貍克剝削，因為現實中的人類為了貍貓的毛皮做出許多殘忍的事... 😅<br />\n <br />\n當然，這個影片同樣引來大量回應嘲諷，畢竟這一切都只是電子遊戲中的虛擬生物，玩家社群似乎早已習慣 PETA 這類的舉動。<br />\n<br />\n所幸，無辜的傅達只是遊戲 NPC 動物，並不會對 PETA 的呼籲有任何反應。唯一可以確定的是，這場突擊抗議沒有造成任何真實動物傷亡，也沒有任何真實動物被解放。"},{"pid":"2e71745cc77ddf5455a36f97d5cc2465992cc84d","tid":2026744,"uid":1121,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:57:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x6qeam0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx6qeam0.png&h=de218e66&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f23282729c3112eee51cc6606f03f5653a720698","tid":2026744,"uid":197477,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:57:59.000Z","msg":"砍樹黎做傢俬都好殘忍<br />\n同埋好唔環保<br />\n整咁多出黎用得曬咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7393062cc5b4dd89e0d7d100d1683cf954ad1b6","tid":2026744,"uid":143474,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:00:57.000Z","msg":"左膠膠到...<br />\n新疆西藏維吾爾族香港咁多人被害又唔出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d504d4a92efaec99fb7e72219de46de928ec1135","tid":2026744,"uid":225347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:00:59.000Z","msg":"痴撚左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ff0b26a75e98a73986f3bd92b82b650ff11cbb","tid":2026744,"uid":56806,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:03:42.000Z","msg":"打GTA又話鼓吹暴力<br />\n連打動森都話叫人路好捉魚捉昆蟲<br />\n<br />\n究竟呢D組織識唔識得分開現實同虛擬世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"393a9e1cc80245bc1d039631a70d0ab6ca90ba6a","tid":2026744,"uid":5320,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:05:18.000Z","msg":"你要捉幾條魚同昆蟲比館長先起到博物館<br />\n姐係PETA都有啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91be5bd5c4b0379df6e6df959cc460aa541c3924","tid":2026744,"uid":7609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:10:47.000Z","msg":"呢d左膠撚樣實事又唔撚做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係弱撚智"},{"pid":"3171d841792e7762ca8b63f475e0cff43c8e2d1a","tid":2026744,"uid":80724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:13:19.000Z","msg":"我真心覺得左膠